CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, December 27, 1952, pg. 17, reads: "They're Happy Too...Billy Eckstine's sister and her family are happy also that the fabulous "Mr. B." will be home for Christmas. Left to right: Mrs. Roland Sawyer, Mr. Sawyer and their daughter, "Stevie." - Teenie Harris Photo.
TitMainTitle: Aileen Eckstein Sawyer, Roland Sawyer, and their daughter "Stevie," posed in living room, horizontal format
